([[名無しさん]] [WEAK[2007-02-22 00:31:45 +00:00]])

[81] [CITE@@en[RFC 2660 - The Secure HyperText Transfer Protocol]]
( ([TIME[2013-07-20 22:21:48 +09:00]] 版))
<http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2660#section-2.6.3.2>
